        'meta_title' => 'Marlboro Country Sagada: Sunrise Hill Loop | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A calm three- to four-hour Sagada loop covering St. Mary\'s Church, Echo Valley hanging coffins, Bokong Falls, and the Marlboro Country grass ridge.',
