        'meta_title' => 'Baguio to Sagada by Bus: GL Trans Honest Guide | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'An honest first-timer guide to the Baguio to Sagada bus on GL Trans, the schedule, the six-hour Halsema ride, and what to expect on arrival.',
