        'meta_title' => 'Sagada or Baguio: Choosing Your Mountain Town | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A calm honest pick between Sagada and Baguio for the first-time Cordillera traveler: time, vibe, activity, climate, and cost compared.',
        'tags' => 'Sagada, Baguio, Cordillera, Mountain Town, Travel Pick',
